race.description: Greyhounds As Pets Mixed Stake Pr2 Division1
race.comment: IS HE LUCKY (1) found some support last start but struggled into fifth (17.04), beaten 1.5 lengths. Was in the money the start prior. Has a solid record from this box including six wins and a minor placing. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. RUPEE MC GRAW (2) had a tricky draw last time when running fourth (22.91) over 395m at Murray Bridge in a Grade 2/3/4. Has a good record at this journey. Consistent performer from this draw with a win and two minor placings to his credit. Expected to run well. STREET BEAST (8) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by a neck at this track in a handy 16.99 beating Kade. Form from his last run is proving strong. Should feature again. OUTSHINE (4) is always a threat when he races at this track and distance. Something for the Multiples: RUPEE MCGRAW (2)

runners.name: Outshine
